The Vaults of Focal the Mad 10

Level 10

General
HistoryThe dungeon was created by mind flayers as a tomb. Its creators were destroyed by internal conflict, and the dungeon has been conquered and altered many times since then.
WallsSuperior Masonry (DC 20 to climb)
FloorUneven Flagstone (DC 10 to charge or run)
TemperatureAverage
IlluminationAverage (shadowy in corridors, lamps or torches in most rooms)
Corridor Features

mThe walls here have been engraved with geometric patterns
nA large demonic idol with ruby eyes sits in an alcove here
rA 10-foot wide chasm cuts across the corridor
sA narrow shaft falls into the corridor from above
uAn unidentifiable odor fills the corridor

xSeveral alcoves are cut into the walls here
zA chute descends from the corridor into the next dungeon level down
